  <text>
    <body>
      <ab type="lido:objectWorkType">Poster</ab>
      <ab subtype="creation" type="lido:event">
        <date>1972 after</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The poster features a collage combining a still from the feature ‘Maestro i Margarita’ (The Master and Margarita) based on a novel by Mikhail Bulgakov and a portrait photograph of director Aleksandar Petrović in the foreground. The leading actors are named in the upper right corner. The logo of Yugoslav distribution company ‘Morava film’ appears in the centre right. Below are the names of the production companies ‘Dunav film’ (Belgrade) and ‘Euro International Films’ (Rome).</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The feature was released in 1972.</ab>
